ree account with Amazon Associates.</p><p>Signing up for the Amazon affiliate program is easy and free.</p><p><a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/associates/join/landing/main.html\">Click here</a> to sign up for Amazon associates. Once you’ve signed up using your email, Amazon will review your application and approve it if you meet the qualifying criteria.</p><p>Just make sure to generate at least THREE sales within the first 180 days.</p><p>Choose the products that are relevant to your blog topics. Then, place the affiliate links on your banners, sidebars, and content to increase click-through rates on your Amazon associate products.</p><p><strong>How do you usually earn from Amazon Associates?</strong></p><p>The Amazon Affiliate program pays on a commission basis, meaning you’ll make a percentage per sale.</p><p>Generally, you earn commissions from qualifying purchases. If someone purchases an Amazon product through your affiliate link, you get a commission. Your Amazon affiliate commission differs based on the product category.</p><p><strong>What’s the Amazon Affiliate program commission structure?</strong></p><p>Here’s an Amazon Affiliate program commission structure chart you can see (to find how much commission you can earn).</p><p><picture><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure.webp 970w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px\"><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure-884x560.png 884w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure-300x190.png 300w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure.png 970w\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px\"><img src=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure-884x560.png\" alt=\"amazon commission structure\" srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure-884x560.png 884w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure-300x190.png 300w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-commission-structure.png 970w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"884\"></picture></p><p>As you can see above, you can earn up to 20% commission through the Amazon affiliate program and most of the categories can fetch you a 4% standard commission.</p><p>So what are you waiting for?</p><p><a href=\"https://affiliate-program.amazon.com/gp/associates/join/landing/main.html\"><strong>Click here</strong></a> to become an Amazon Affiliate for FREE</p><p><strong>How does Amazon pay its referrers?</strong></p><p>Amazon pays you each and every month and the minimum payment threshold limit is $100. You can withdraw the money in 3 different ways including an Amazon gift card, direct deposit (US-based associates only), and check.</p><h2><strong>7 Best Practices to Make Money from Amazon Affiliate Program</strong></h2><p>Are you looking for the best practices and tips on how to make money from the Amazon affiliate program? Here are a few PROVEN ways to increase your Amazon Associates commissions in 2022.</p><h3><strong>1. Sell low-ticket products when starting out</strong></h3><p>One of the best ways to increase your Amazon affiliate sales is to sell cheaper products in the beginning and then refer to higher-priced products.</p><p>Refer products with lower price tags (such as eBooks) to increase your volume every month to increase your overall average commission from Amazon associates.&nbsp;</p><p>Let us explain this in a simple example.</p><p>Amazon gives you a 4% commission per every product you sell if you are selling 1 to 6 products from Amazon associates each month.&nbsp;</p><p>If you’re selling high-priced products, you may not be able to make more than 5 sales each month being a beginner. So you’ll earn not more than 4% on each product you sell that is highly-priced.</p><p>But if you first sell the products with less price tag, you can increase your overall average commission, then if you can make a handful of high-priced products, you can easily hit 6% commission.&nbsp;</p><p>Here’s the percentage referral fee is given by Amazon associates (volume-based commission for general products).</p><p><picture><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission.webp 455w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px\"><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission.png 455w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission-300x193.png 300w\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 455px) 100vw, 455px\"><img src=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission.png\" alt=\"amazon referral commission\" srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission.png 455w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/amazon-referral-commission-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"455\"></picture></p><p>So if you’re selling 5 cheap products on average and 2 or higher priced products, you’ll be getting an average commission of 6%.</p><h3><strong>2. Write genuine product reviews</strong></h3><p>The surefire way to increase your Amazon associate earnings is to write reviews about the<a href=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/how-to-sell-affiliate-products/\"> products you promote</a>.&nbsp;</p><p>Writing unbiased product reviews can help your readers to better understand your products.</p><p><strong>Why write product reviews?</strong></p><p>They can help you educate your audience about the products you promote.</p><p>Make sure to write reviews that offer value. List out all the pros and cons along with the alternatives.</p><p>If you show the benefits of the products you promote, your audience will engage more. If they see value in your products, your Amazon associates income will increase. Make sure to test out the products before you promote them from your product reviews.</p><p>Few product vendors offer free trials (especially software vendors). So you can ask for a product demo and share the pros and cons of the products from product reviews. This will give you an edge in converting readers to buyers to boost your Amazon affiliate sales.</p><p>Here’s an example;</p><p>We use Semrush (#1 SEO tool) almost daily and we partnered with them to provide a <a href=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/semrush-coupon/\">special Semrush coupon</a> to give a 30-day FREE Semrush trial to our users.</p><p>Now, all our website users can enjoy the <a href=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/unbiased-semrush-review/\">Semrush tool free for 30 days</a>.</p><p><picture><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon.webp 900w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px\"><source srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon-884x666.png 884w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon-300x226.png 300w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon.png 900w\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px\"><img src=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon-884x666.png\" alt=\"semrush coupon\" srcset=\"https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon-884x666.png 884w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon-300x226.png 300w, https://bloggerspassion.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/semrush-coupon.png 900w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"884\"></picture></p>',3,'2022-08-12 07:17:00','2022-08-12 10:28:40'),(5,'How to Start a Lifestyle Blog','how-to-start-a-lifestyle-blog','<p>Do you want to start a lifestyle blog the right way? You’re in the right place.</p><p>We know th